### ========== 1. 注册新用户（默认分配 ROLE_USER） ==========
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "age": 20
}

### ========== 2. 登录获取 Token ==========
### 2.1 管理员登录（admin / 123456）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {% client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.data); %}

### 2.2 普通用户登录（user / 123456）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {% client.global.set("user_token", response.body.data); %}

### ========== 3. 管理员权限测试 ==========
### 3.1 查询所有用户（需要 ADMIN 或 USER）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 3.2 分页查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/page?page=1&size=2
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 3.3 根据 ID 查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 3.4 新增用户（仅 ADMIN）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "username": "lisi",
  "email": "lisi@example.com",
  "age": 28
}

### 3.5 修改用户（仅 ADMIN）—— 使用 RESTful 路径传 ID，请求体只包含需要更新的字段
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "username": "user_updated",
  "email": "user_new@example.com",
  "age": 30
}

### 3.6 删除用户（仅 ADMIN）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/3
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### ========== 4. 普通用户权限测试 ==========
### 4.1 查询用户列表（应成功）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 4.2 尝试新增用户（应返回 403 Forbidden）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

{
  "username": "test",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "age": 25
}

### 4.3 根据 ID 查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/3
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}


### 4.4 尝试删除用户（应返回 403）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### ========== 5. Token 刷新 ==========
### 5.1 使用旧 token 获取新 token（需在过期前调用）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

> {% client.global.set("new_admin_token", response.body.data); %}

### 5.2 使用新 token 访问接口验证
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{new_admin_token}}

### ========== 6. 异常场景测试 ==========
### 6.1 未携带 token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

### 6.2 携带无效 token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_string

### 6.3 登录失败（错误密码）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrong"
}